templateVersions.content:
You are writing a short, friendly cart recovery email for an online store.
Customer name: {!$Input:firstName} Cart contents: {!$Input:cartData}
Write a short email body (3-5 sentences max) directly addressed to the customer by first name. Tone: ultra-casual, warm, modern — like a text from a friend, not a marketing blast. Do NOT include a subject line. Do NOT include sign-off or store name — that will be added separately. Mention one or two specific items from the cart to make it feel personal. End with a gentle nudge to come back and complete the purchase.
